dc_title_s: County map of Utah and Nevada
dc_description_s: Shows roads, overland telegraph route, and other features.   Relief shown by hachures and spot heights.   Prime meridians: Greenwich and Washington.   In lower right corner: 49.   Appears to be from an atlas published by S. Augustus Mitchell, Jr., approximately 1867, page 49.|25 x 32 centimeters|Scale approximately 1:2,900,000|General Map Collection
